node.text: ❤️🍫🙌🏻BEST CHOCOLATE CAKE!!! The secret ingredient? Ricotta cheese! Makes it extra moist and flavorful! Full recipe and video on my website! https://bakerbynature.com/chocolate-ricotta-layer-cake/

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ashley | Baker By Nature on August 03, 2021. May be an image of cupcake.

node.text: Healthy Bakery-Style Chocolate Chip Muffins?! Yes, please! These are a bbn community favorite… and for good reasons! They’re fluffy, perfectly sweet, and loaded with just the right amount of chocolate chips! https://bakerbynature.com/healthy-bakery-style-chocolate-chip-muffins/

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ashley | Baker By Nature on August 02, 2021. May be an image of dessert.

node.text: ❤️🍫Chocolate Mascarpone Cheesecake! Unapologetically decadent and definitely for chocolate lovers only! This make-ahead friendly dessert is always a showstopper! https://bakerbynature.com/chocolate-mascarpone-cheesecake/

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ashley | Baker By Nature on August 01, 2021. May be an image of food and drink.

node.text: It’s a good day to sit in the sun and sip Spicy Jalapeño Margaritas!!! Super easy, refreshing, and serves a crowd! https://bakerbynature.com/spicy-jalapeno-margaritas-for-a-crowd/?swcfpc=1

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ashley | Baker By Nature on August 01, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: 🧀Zucchini CHEDDAR Scones!!! If you’ve never made savory scones before, consider this your invitation to give it a try! Soft, fluffy, cheesy, and so delicious! These are a great way to use up an abundance of Summer squash! https://bakerbynature.com/zucchini-cheddar-scones/

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ashley | Baker By Nature on July 31, 2021. May be an image of dessert and indoor.

node.text: ❤️🍪🍫Easy Chocolate Chip Cookie Bars! Everything you love about chocolate chip cookies but SO much easier! Delicious with ice cream, too! https://bakerbynature.com/easy-chocolate-chip-cookie-bars/

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ashley | Baker By Nature on July 31, 2021. May be an image of strawberry and dessert.

node.text: 🍓💕Strawberries & Cream Scones! Not dry and boring like a lot of other scones! Instead, these beauties are soft, buttery, and loaded with juicy strawberries! The sticky glaze is perfectly sweet and a total treat! https://bakerbynature.com/strawberries-and-cream-scones/?swcfpc=1

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Ashley | Baker By Nature on July 30, 2021 tagging @doriatlove, and @rikkisnyder. May be an image of 1 person, food and indoor.

node.text: 🍦🍪Ice Cream Sandwiches are always a good idea! So today I’m sharing my Top 10 BEST Cookies for Homemade Ice Cream Sandwiches! Plus, some fun ice cream pairing ideas! https://bakerbynature.com/top-10-best-cookies-for-homemade-ice-cream-sandwiches/

node.text: Tiramisu to celebrate the weekend ☕️🎉 This ULTRA creamy, yet light and refreshing treat is this is the PERFECT Summer dessert! And it’s make-ahead friendly, too! https://bakerbynature.com/italian-tiramisu-for-a-crowd/
